          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>💜 <strong>Amethyst is here to awaken the calm power that already lives within you.</strong></h2><p>It’s the crystal of deep restoration — a key to your inner peace, intuition, and mental clarity.<br/><br/>Instead of igniting chaos, it silences the noise. It reconnects you to the part of yourself that already knows — and always did.</p><h3><strong>NOTE: All our crystals are genuine.</strong></h3><p>Amethyst naturally comes in a range of shades — from pale lilac to deep royal violet, sometimes with soft white or smoky bands.</p><p><strong>You will always receive the crystal that’s meant for your energy.</strong></p><p>If you just want a perfectly colored, synthetic purple gem — please order a plastic one online. We don’t sell imitations.</p><p>We only offer products to customers who understand that every stone we craft comes directly from <strong>Mother Earth</strong>, not a factory.</p><p>Each piece is unique, imperfect, and alive — shaped by time, pressure, and silence.</p><p>You can see the different tones and natural patterns in the picture below — that’s what makes each <strong>Amethyst</strong> piece truly yours.</p>"
          }
        }
