            "text": "<h3>💜 <strong>Why is this necklace more expensive?</strong></h3><p>Authentic <strong>Amethyst</strong> of deep violet quality is becoming harder to find — true volcanic-origin stones are now considered semi-precious, and their price continues to rise.</p><p>Be cautious if you see “cheap amethyst” — it’s often <strong>dyed quartz, glass, or synthetic crystal</strong>, not the real thing.</p><p>And trust us — it won’t carry the same <strong>energy, healing frequency, or calming effects AT ALL!</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      },
