    "testimonials_UrzVVB": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "column_yN4mgL": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>I placed it in my living room, but now I move it wherever I go. The amethyst energy is simply divine,  it fills the room with calm and harmony every time I turn it on</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Laura M.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_GLPTqN": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Sophisticated, serene, and deeply spiritual. It’s not just beautiful, it truly shifts the energy of the space. The light is gentle and soothing, perfect for evening reflection or quiet reading.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Michael R.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_fC4EQq": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>What started as a lamp became my evening ritual. Every night I turn it on before journaling. It helps me center my thoughts and release the stress of the day.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Evelyn H.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_m8Dadf": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 4,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>A perfect balance of art and energy. I’ve always loved modern design with spiritual symbolism. This lamp brings both, light for the eyes, peace for the soul.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>David L.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_aL4BaM": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Didn’t expect much when I ordered it, but it honestly moved me. There’s something in the glow that brings deep comfort. My husband, who doesn’t believe in crystals at all, said he sleeps better when it’s on.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Sophia G.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_mEFwAM": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>A constant reminder to slow down and breathe. The moment I come home and switch it on, the world quiets down. It’s like having a personal sanctuary of light.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Janet P.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_zh4Efj": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Finally, a product that radiates both quality and soul. The craftsmanship is exquisite, and the soft energy it emits feels cleansing. You can tell it was made with intention.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Anthony D.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_fdzD4Y": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Illuminates not just the room, but your spirit. I use it in my yoga space. It transformed the entire vibe, now the room feels grounded and sacred.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Martha S.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_GAfM9Y": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>My little temple of silence. When I’m overwhelmed, I sit beside it and just breathe. The gentle light feels like therapy.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Patricia W.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_y4i4md": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>More than decor, you can truly feel its presence. As a therapist, I use it in my practice. Clients often comment how peaceful the energy feels before our sessions begin.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Richard K.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_iYYLA4": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 4,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Perfect for evening rituals and deep relaxation. The 30 light modes offer so many moods, from soft golden warmth to a mystical violet glow. My favorite for meditation time.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Clara J.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_DnN94Q": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>A symbol of infinity that reminds me how everything is connected. The halo shape and crystals create a constant flow of gentle, circular energy. It’s pure feng shui magic.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Elizabeth N.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_LQKYpX": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 4,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>Bought it as a gift for my sister and now I want one too. Her reaction was priceless ,she said it felt like her home started breathing again.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Liam B.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_mX6A3r": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>My house has never felt this peaceful. The light is soothing, the energy feels healing, and the design fits any room beautifully.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Diana C.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_Jy8EGU": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>For those who seek harmony without sacrificing aesthetics. It looks like a designer piece but radiates with spiritual calm. Truly the best of both worlds.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Mark F.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_HjYEqm": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>It’s as if the light itself is meditating. I placed it near the window, when the sun sets, the halo glow creates a magical atmosphere that’s hard to describe.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Helen T.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_Xh3zfH": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 4,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>The most elegant Feng Shui addition to my home. I placed it by the entrance, and now it feels like stepping into peace every time I come home.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>James P.</strong>"
          }
        },
        "column_hF4j99": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "star_rating": 5,
            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>My nightly affirmation has finally found its anchor. As the light flickers softly, I repeat: ‘I am at ease with life and make peace with everyone and everything.’ And somehow, peace really does come effortlessly.</p>",
            "author": "<strong>Rachel M.</strong>"
          }
        }
      },
